name: Forgotten Persona #2
description:
Animated GIF | 8 fps| 2048 x 2048 | RGB | sRGB IEC61966-2.1 

A woman I have never met and who may not even exist. She exists only in my memories of old black and white photos I saw in my childhood. By drawing all 4 images at once, I found an approach to recreate a memory of a forgotten person without knowing what she really looks like. Like any faded memory, none of these portraits is an exact copy of the other. Only a memory of the human mind.
